Package: DP.lasso
Type: Package
Title: Discriminative power lasso (DP-lasso)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: 
    c(person(given = "Cornelia",
           family = "Fuetterer",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "corneliafuetterer@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8354-6660")), 
	person(given = "Ruth", family = "Pfeiffer", role = c("aut"), email = "pfeiffer@mail.nih.gov",
                    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7791-2698")))
Maintainer: Cornelia Fuetterer <corneliafuetterer@gmail.com>
Description: DP-lasso is a regularized regression approach for multinomial logistic models for categorical outcomes with a novel adaptive L1-type  penalty term,that incorporates ANOVA based weights (DPan). We also provide clustering based DP-lasso approaches using the Daavies-Bouldin (DB) index, and the Silhouette index (Si), resulting in DPdb and DPsi.
